{"tid":1738020,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"終於知點解無白警!!!!","createTime":"2019-11-19T06:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T06:50:05.000Z","uid":19002,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc1c7841808f6361e1484a0b29367b85ddea9dd","tid":1738020,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"因為只要班白警話有野做得唔岩<br />\n班黑警就會屌佢地做分化撚<br />\n係未想搞衰大家士氣<br />\n<br />\n做得唔岩檢討有咩問題?<br />\n我同意有部分人語氣好重<br />\n但同時亦都有一班人唔係好接受到意見<br />\n提出意見檢討唔係分化<br />\n希望大家留意"},{"pid":"0357ef7a935e3457f637068db237fd665ef3e30e","tid":1738020,"uid":308595,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"白警死哂<br />\n黑警死全家"},{"pid":"dfaf50bdd3e43f29b14526037536e71540a63d55","tid":1738020,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"因為人地有糧出有宿舍有福利可以為所欲為"},{"pid":"235db9fb8e48e0a6d8b50a1e36a4a748e9ba2ebf","tid":1738020,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"無用架 講野唔岩聽就話你分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3b7516a9a5d3388ff019dc636934a60feba687","tid":1738020,"uid":112622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43dbda87fba7aa202c5725d63d0771dbeaa38881","tid":1738020,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b88bcd46a415144c49bc87140f4cf3cf7255be0","tid":1738020,"uid":340080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPs9Dbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPs9Dbb.jpg&h=156a488c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb47a466b784f811e1fee9ff7617c1c44f0da90c","tid":1738020,"uid":3522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:24:45.000Z","msg":"近排情況越黎越嚴重<br />\n一旦見到相反意見，就一句：<br />\n「五毛」、「分化撚」、「散水撚」<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就：<br />\n「上前線講」<br />\n「前線自己決定」<br />\n「hello sir」"},{"pid":"0a778070b2e772f7bc9d5f4bee7049cfb353dd7d","tid":1738020,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"18-8-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"34903cc4abbf159234d2db281f54be6c0d05e758","tid":1738020,"uid":216683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:29:38.000Z","msg":"人地黑警士氣勁到痴線<br />\n因為佢地唔會屌自己友<br />\n做錯, 咪睇下點樣補獲, 但唔會屌佢, 唔會話佢係鬼<br />\n<br />\n連登、冷氣軍師?<br />\n講到大條道理, 又話咁唔岩呢樣又唔岩<br />\n未落過場就話, 唔應該咁做, 應該要點做<br />\n但其實無諗過落場同睇LIVE個差別係邊<br />\n<br />\n俾幾個例子你<br />\n冷氣軍師: 其實大家唔洗驚唔洗退, 每人都拎棍同佢打近戰, 只要唔退一齊衝就會贏<br />\n現實: 對家拎住AR15自動步槍, 成班人一齊衝就開實彈掃射, 唔會衝到埋去, 仲有無限粒橡膠彈同平射TG<br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍師: 去到宜家都仲未見到漆彈, 識唔識玩架你地<br />\n現實: 漆彈, 有高空優勢會有用, 但宜家係打馬路戰, 平地。漆彈射程用人力掉出去20米內, 但同班狗距離最少50米, 點掉? 你跑出去掉, 幾十粒橡膠彈打埋黎。睇LIVE好似好近, 跑前幾步就夠近, 但佢地永遠唔會諗現場跑, 其實個距離係子彈限制咗<br />\n<br />\n結論: 一班存在係唔同世界, 唔同環境嘅人係到指指點點, 又話乜又話物, 之後就話討論有咩問題。個問題就係大家根本企係唔到位置, 點討論都唔會有結論。你要講建議, 其實落一次場, 我相信落完一次就會有真正好嘅建議出黎。"},{"pid":"2fe56c88aa2dc93bdd04fb3d7cd4300a9882fd04","tid":1738020,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0357ef7a935e3457f637068db237fd665ef3e30e","tid":1738020,"uid":308595,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"白警死哂<br />\n黑警死全家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"6月都quit啦白警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4587fdd186722d8e54062878a5cc4e8b507124d","tid":1738020,"uid":221846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:36:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">其實可唔可以po上weibo</span><br />\n<br />\n[核彈] 有關新彊集中營既中共內部文件流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737558</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a953c71b2da655e91c1ebc7f2ef61be7565dbdd9","tid":1738020,"uid":72381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"無白警你老豆搵仔D料點黎？<br />\n只係白警都唔係好人姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用腦"},{"pid":"1f9918b548c175b1201aec63b6657509a303ab44","tid":1738020,"uid":19002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a953c71b2da655e91c1ebc7f2ef61be7565dbdd9","tid":1738020,"uid":72381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"無白警你老豆搵仔D料點黎？<br />\n只係白警都唔係好人姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用腦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:41:05.000Z","msg":"咁班白警夠唔夠膽當著啲狗面前講佢地做錯？"},{"pid":"61c0abe10838de902d1bd0d5b327a70adddbaf8c","tid":1738020,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:45:10.000Z","msg":"會唔會一早俾人溶晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d9ba443d7371fb0775ec46fe9479de3cb4cffa9","tid":1738020,"uid":282118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:50:05.000Z","msg":"話白警死晒嗰啲究竟明唔明樓主嘅重點係乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主要再講清楚啲"}]}